{"lastModified":null,"uri":"c::7819256863::vessel::e0c4b530-d516-11f0-b973-071e2633a35d","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Summer/Winter Operating Area: Aegean and Mediterrenean, Greek Islands\n\nPhantom Spook 62 – Anchor the Moment\n\nBlending elegance and performance, the Phantom Spook 62 delivers an exceptional yachting experience with its 18.5-meter length and robust hull design. Powered by twin Volvo Penta D8 diesel engines producing a total of 1200 hp, this luxury yacht reaches a cruising speed of 24 knots and a top speed of 26 knots, offering both safety and thrill at sea.\n\nInside, two en-suite guest cabins, a modern galley, and a spacious salon create a refined living space, while the Burmese teak deck adds timeless elegance and durability.\n\nWith approximately 2000 liters of fuel and 2500 liters of fresh water capacity, the Phantom Spook 62 is designed for both long-range voyages and short escapes. Advanced navigation systems, expansive deck areas, and premium equipment ensure every journey is unforgettable.\n\nPhantom Spook 62 – Anchor the Moment.\nSet your dreams at sea, and enjoy the freedom of the moment.","blueprint":{"name":"PHANTOM","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::e0c4b530-d516-11f0-b973-071e2633a35d::assets::18bcb920-d51b-11f0-b19a-7fcb4bc97c63/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e0c4b530-d516-11f0-b973-071e2633a35d::assets::18c125f0-d51b-11f0-b19a-7fcb4bc97c63/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e0c4b530-d516-11f0-b973-071e2633a35d::assets::18b78900-d51b-11f0-b19a-7fcb4bc97c63/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e0c4b530-d516-11f0-b973-071e2633a35d::assets::18a51270-d51b-11f0-b19a-7fcb4bc97c63/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e0c4b530-d516-11f0-b973-071e2633a35d::assets::18bdca90-d51b-11f0-b19a-7fcb4bc97c63/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e0c4b530-d516-11f0-b973-071e2633a35d::assets::18c6f250-d51b-11f0-b19a-7fcb4bc97c63/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::